flowchart TD
    A[Student opens assessment intro] --> B[Click Start Assessment]
    B --> C[Create new assessment attempt]
    C --> D[Set started_at, expires_at, status]
    D --> E[Load first page]
    E --> F[Student answers questions]
    F --> G[Autosave answers]
    G --> H[Update progress]
    H --> I{More pages?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Move to next or previous page]
    J --> F
    I -->|No| K{Submit manually?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Submit assessment]
    K -->|No| M{Time expired?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Auto submit assessment]
    M -->|No| F
    L --> O[Calculate score]
    N --> O
    O --> P[Update assessment progress]
    P --> Q[Show result screen]